        <num>CCP 859</num>
        <heading>859.  Same; judgment or decision</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 859.  Same; judgment or decision
In pleading a judgment of a domestic or foreign court, or a decision of a judicial or quasi judicial tribunal, or of a board, commission, or officer, it is sufficient to allege the judgment or decision without setting forth matter showing jurisdiction to render it.</p>
        </content>
